<h3>Introduction</h3>
<desc>
    The <strong>ui-list</strong> Ember-CLI addon is a set components meant to help you manage lists in your applications. Lists are everywhere and therefore it
    is our selfish hope that this addon is soon everywhere too but regardless of its distribution, here's what it does ...
</desc>

<h3>Components</h3>
<desc>
    The typical usage -- or at least the most compact/simplist usage -- is inline use of the "LIST" components. These in turn will manage the ITEMs and
    leverage HELPERs where appropriate. Still you may go into any level of detail you like, click on any of the components below to get
    design details and interactive examples. Interactive examples? How lucky are you? Yes the world is finally giving back. You're a consumer.
    Your job is now clear ... start clicking on components.
</desc>
